description:
It was discovered that Kamailio incorrectly handled a specially crafted file.
An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause a denial of service or
other unspecified impact.

kamailio.description: very fast and configurable SIP proxy

title: Kamailio vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary: kamailio could be made to crash if it opened a specially crafted file.
